    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine has had an initial 15 min, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and press the<strong> </strong>aubergine flesh down firmly with a fork to release the juices (this will help them cook quicker!)</p><p>Add the <strong>butternut squash cubes</strong> to the tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven for 15 min further or until the aubergine flesh has softened and the butternut squash is tender</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1609945051270-x200.jpg",
