            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is almost cooked, stir through the <strong>aubergine purée </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min</p><p>Tear in the <strong>basil leaves</strong> and gently mix everything together – this is your<strong> aubergine risotto</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p><p>Wash the <strong>salad</strong>, then pat them dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
