            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1609945424119-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>aubergine risotto</strong> topped with the <strong>roasted butternut squash</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining toasted pine nuts </strong>and the <strong>salad</strong>, then season with a few grinds of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and a little<strong> olive oil</strong> over the salad and serve the <strong>lemon wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
